{
  "page": "Jack",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Jack</b> and its variants are a common male name. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Cutjack\" title=\"Cutjack\">Cutjack</a>, a recruit for the Night’s Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ginger_Jack\" title=\"Ginger Jack\">Ginger Jack</a>, a sellsword with the Windblown</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nine-Finger_Jack\" title=\"Nine-Finger Jack\">Nine-Finger Jack</a>, a legendary hero of the Riverlands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Jack_Crabb\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Red Jack Crabb\">Red Jack Crabb</a>, a member of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jack-Be-Lucky\" title=\"Jack-Be-Lucky\">Jack-Be-Lucky</a>, a member of the brotherhood without banners</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jack_Bulwer\" title=\"Jack Bulwer\">Jack Bulwer</a>, called \"Black Jack\", a ranger of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jack_Musgood\" title=\"Jack Musgood\">Jack Musgood</a>, called \"Sleepy Jack\", a former Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jack&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jace_(Night%27s_Watch)\" title=\"Jace (Night&#39;s Watch)\">Jace</a>, a recruit of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jacaerys_Velaryon\" title=\"Jacaerys Velaryon\">Jacaerys Velaryon</a>, called \"Jace\", the firstborn son of Princess Rhaenyra Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jacks\" title=\"Jacks\">Jacks</a>, a guard sworn to House Stark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jax\" title=\"Jax\">Jax</a>, a wildling</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jyck\" title=\"Jyck\">Jyck</a>, a guard sworn to House Lannister</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404055057\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.005 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:14715-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404055057 and revision id 323502\n -->\n",
